headline: 1 Reason to Like PYPL and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: PayPal has gotten torched over the last six months - since August 2025, its stock price has dropped 38.8% to $41.65 per share. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
